refreshType.description: The type of refresh that the dataset undergoes. Valid values are `INCREMENTAL_REFRESH` and `FULL_REFRESH`.

scheduleFrequency.description: The configuration of the [schedule frequency](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/quicksight/latest/APIReference/API_RefreshFrequency.html). See schedule_frequency.

startAfterDateTime.description: Time after which the refresh schedule can be started, expressed in `YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SS` format.
